{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/portfolios/casavida-customer-relationship-management-console","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e9448505-525a-5040-ba01-6c8903666afb","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/473a63df8ab520d36309cb2c1996b6c9/351ee/health-condition-dashboard-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.12500000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"health condition dashboard 2\"\n        title=\"health condition dashboard 2\"\n        src=\"/static/473a63df8ab520d36309cb2c1996b6c9/6af66/health-condition-dashboard-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/473a63df8ab520d36309cb2c1996b6c9/69538/health-condition-dashboard-2.png 160w,\n/static/473a63df8ab520d36309cb2c1996b6c9/72799/health-condition-dashboard-2.png 320w,\n/static/473a63df8ab520d36309cb2c1996b6c9/6af66/health-condition-dashboard-2.png 640w,\n/static/473a63df8ab520d36309cb2c1996b6c9/d9199/health-condition-dashboard-2.png 960w,\n/static/473a63df8ab520d36309cb2c1996b6c9/21b4d/health-condition-dashboard-2.png 1280w,\n/static/473a63df8ab520d36309cb2c1996b6c9/351ee/health-condition-dashboard-2.png 3350w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Employer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>La Vida Tec Co., Ltd</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Targeted Users:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Health institutes</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>User Scenarios:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>CasaVida represented a <strong>Customer Relationship Management(CRM) console</strong> for health institutes.\nThe dashboard of Personal Health Records(PHRs) and charts helped admins recognizing patients’ health risks.\nMoreover, admins could create accounts for patients and send coupons to attract patients to use telemedicine services.\nThus, CasaVida could save health institutes lots of efforts for patients management and strengthen their relationships.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Programming Language:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>TypeScript</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Libraries:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>axios</li>\n<li>firebase</li>\n<li>koa</li>\n<li>next</li>\n<li>next-i18next</li>\n<li>node-forge</li>\n<li>react</li>\n<li>react-redux</li>\n<li>redux</li>\n<li>react-dom</li>\n<li>redux-persist</li>\n<li>redux-persist-transform-encrypt</li>\n<li>redux-saga</li>\n<li>reselect</li>\n<li>styled-components</li>\n<li>styled-system</li>\n<li>tus-js-client</li>\n<li>typescript</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Features：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Configured the TypeScript support for Next.js 8</li>\n<li>Developed the member system to verify experts’ accounts through cookies and the local storage</li>\n<li>Developed a video uploading feature by implementing the streaming library “tus-js-client”</li>\n<li>Developed account importing feature to help institutes creating patients’ accounts\n<div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem\" > <div class=\"embedVideo-container\"> <iframe title=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/590621135\" class=\"embedVideo-iframe\" style=\"border:0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen=\"\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups\"></iframe> </div> </div></li>\n<li>Developed activate account feature for patients to receive coupons\n<div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem\" > <div class=\"embedVideo-container\"> <iframe title=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/590621620\" class=\"embedVideo-iframe\" style=\"border:0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen=\"\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups\"></iframe> </div> </div></li>\n<li>Implemented cryptographic algorithms such as ECC, RSA, and AES to secure sensitive data</li>\n<li>Implemented D3.js to visualize personal health records</li>\n<li>Supported English and Chinese language display</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Product Released on Oct 2, 2019</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/portfolios/casavida-customer-relationship-management-console","tagSlugs":null},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-08-23T09:10:00.100Z","description":"A customer relationship management console for health experts or institutes.","tags":null,"title":"CasaVida: Customer Relationship Management Console","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/473a63df8ab520d36309cb2c1996b6c9/health-condition-dashboard-2.png"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/portfolios/casavida-customer-relationship-management-console"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3983120721","401334301"]}